00:41:10.080 --> 00:41:12.290
Two, a knife.

00:41:12.290 --> 00:41:15.100
Forschner makes a Victorinox
Fibrox knife.

00:41:15.100 --> 00:41:16.670
It's $25.

00:41:16.670 --> 00:41:19.610
It beats the $150 knives
all the time.

00:41:19.610 --> 00:41:23.090
Third thing is knife
sharpening.

00:41:23.090 --> 00:41:26.220
Jacques Pepin would die if I
