00:41:40.780 --> 00:41:42.510
One last thing.

00:41:42.510 --> 00:41:45.970
The European knives have a
20 degree angle to them.

00:41:45.970 --> 00:41:50.180
The combination east west knives
have a 15 degree angle.

00:41:50.180 --> 00:41:57.070
